<img src="http://leadersandco.s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/23030037/Computer-Professionals-Registration-Council-of-Nigeria-CPN-696x464.jpg" />  The Theme for the 2018 IT Professionals’ Assembly is, “Professionalism in Information Technology; Past, Present and Future.” The 2018 Assembly which coincides with the 25th Anniversary Celebration of CPN holds in Abuja from Wednesday 20th – Thursday 21st June, 2018. The venue is at the Abuja International Conference Centre, Central Area, Area 11, 900, Herbert Macaulay Way, Abuja. Participants at this year’s Assembly would be given Tablets already pre-loaded with the event App, Papers to be delivered and the three Programmes of Event (Induction Programme, IT Assembly programme and the Annual General Report). Suleiman idris is a graduate of Fed Univ of Tech Minna (BTECH Mathematics/Comp Science), Specialist in ICT Support Services. also proficient in use of online journalism tools & Social media management. I currently serve as I.T Officer with Africa's Largest TV Network NTA